<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span> صحيح ـ <span class="c2">((ظلال الجنة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٧٣٩)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ أَبُو حَاتِمٍ:</span> الصُّنابِح: مِن الصَّحَابَةِ. ⦗٣٨٦⦘<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
